text:
(upbeat music)
- Hi,
I am Rajat Bhardwaj.

I work as an Enterprise
Support Manager with AWS.

Today, we have the pleasure
to host Neeraj Chauhan,
who is the CIO at PayU India,

to talk about their journey
with Enterprise Support.
Neeraj, if you can share your experience
how Enterprise Support helped you

to achieve your business
critical outcomes.
- Thanks, Rajat.
Hello, everyone.
I'm proud to say that PayU is

the leading payment
solution provider in India.

With our innovative solutions,
we are trusted partner
of over five lakh businesses in India,

ensuring seamless and secure
online payment transactions.
Our organization's main challenge is

to manage operations in
a cost effective, secure,

and efficient manner
that can scale quickly.

AWS Enterprise Support has
played a very crucial role

in achieving those objectives
by providing packet

of proactive services and
access to technical expertise.

With the help of our
Technical Account Managers,

TAM has been always our
trusted advisor guiding us
through complex technical challenges

and ensuring we improve
our security posture,
resilience, optimize our cost.
With the help of Enterprise Support

and our trusted partner or TAM
and Enterprise Support Team,
we were able to reduce or optimize
our cost by more than 100k per month.
Thank you.
Thank you so much for enabling us.
(upbeat music)
